{"tid":2232174,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"Marketing書推薦：最近買左呢本書睇，想睇薦比大家","createTime":"2020-10-06T08:11:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T08:15:16.000Z","uid":265117,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4c739c9174b725ab110a4b1dd1fa2729c7486d52","tid":2232174,"uid":265117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T08:11:31.000Z","msg":"第一次係度分享書，希望幫到大家。<br />\n<br />\n今日想同大家分享一本我最近覺得幾唔錯嘅一本Marketing書：<br />\n<br />\n《One Million Followers 百萬粉絲經營法則》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://im2.book.com.tw/image/getImage?i=https://www.books.com.tw/img/001/086/30/0010863027_bc_01.jpg&amp;v=5ef9d0e8&amp;w=348&amp;h=348\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fim2.book.com.tw%2Fimage%2FgetImage%3Fi%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.books.com.tw%2Fimg%2F001%2F086%2F30%2F0010863027_bc_01.jpg%26v%3D5ef9d0e8%26w%3D348%26h%3D348&h=75cad6b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.books.com.tw/products/0010863027?sloc=main\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.books.com.tw%2Fproducts%2F0010863027%3Fsloc%3Dmain&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKKf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=75b4dd7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.books.com.tw/products/0010863027?sloc=main</a><br />\n<br />\n我前兩日買左，用左三日時間睇晒，因為入面講嘅野幾實用，真係睇完唔會得個睇字。<br />\n<br />\n好多關於marketing嘅書，最鍾意就係講呢句：「你要用心做Contents。只要contents好，你嘅觀眾就會感受到，假以時日，你就可以建立到一個品牌。」<br />\n<br />\n呢句野冇錯，但係具體咩野係「Content好」？<br />\n<br />\n呢本書就講到比我地知點樣為之好嘅contents，答案就係透過測試、測試同埋測試。<br />\n<br />\n舉例黎講，你想開一個IG帳號分享書評，開左個帳號同埋出左幾個post之後，作者建議：<br />\n<br />\n1. 先定義persona（書入面有好多題目幫你諗）<br />\n2. 落廣告測試<br />\n3. 搵出鐘意同埋會分享你內容嘅觀眾<br />\n<br />\n呢個過程就係：提出假設、實驗同埋優化或轉向。<br />\n<br />\n「假設書評嘅post有好多18-34歲嘅後生仔女鍾意睇」然後將個post放係IG、FB落廣告。（實驗）如果係用左$50之後，冇人理個廣告、沒有like同埋share，就可以諗下：<br />\n<br />\n1. 係咪內容出錯？<br />\n2. 係咪觀眾設定出錯？<br />\n3. 修改內容，再重新出post<br />\n<br />\n呢個就係成本書教嘅核心。亦係成本書嘅重點。<br />\n<br />\n呢本書嘅作者真係係fb、ig都有過百萬粉絲，我覺得信得過。<br />\n<br />\n希望呢個post嘅介紹同埋呢本書可以幫到各位有Youtube Channel、IG或者Facebook page嘅朋友。"},{"pid":"504ea3697e884b3938109cfbaae7beb2649481de","tid":2232174,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T08:12:22.000Z","msg":"都係睇返車sir啲course好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b536a4f6ae373bd30d143aaf7506490ce8e3bc","tid":2232174,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T08:12:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41e49ceb8a4576b5ee90b1ba111d632c100abbe0","tid":2232174,"uid":265117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"504ea3697e884b3938109cfbaae7beb2649481de","tid":2232174,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T08:12:22.000Z","msg":"都係睇返車sir啲course好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T08:15:16.000Z","msg":"Quit左youtube，睇唔到😢😢"}]}